Min-ho, never forget
that this is thanks to me.

4
00:00:12,887 --> 00:00:13,722
Thank you.

5
00:00:17,183 --> 00:00:19,436
-I put your photo up in the science room.
-Min-ho.

6
00:00:19,519 --> 00:00:21,646
Do you want to be a scientist
like Yun-sang?

7
00:00:21,730 --> 00:00:24,107
No, this is more like a fan thing.

8
00:00:25,775 --> 00:00:28,528
-Beer tastes best after soccer.
-It sure does!

9
00:00:29,487 --> 00:00:30,989
-Hi!
-Father Baek's here.

10
00:00:31,072 --> 00:00:31,948
-Father.
-Yes?

11
00:00:32,032 --> 00:00:33,783
So did you win your revenge match?

12
00:00:33,867 --> 00:00:34,701
Revenge match?

13
00:00:35,493 --> 00:00:36,327
-Father Woo.
-Yes?

14
00:00:36,411 --> 00:00:37,412
Have a beer.

15
00:00:37,495 --> 00:00:39,748
He started out strong,
but I caught up to him.

16
00:00:40,248 --> 00:00:42,208
You must be boiling inside.

17
00:00:42,292 --> 00:00:45,086
Father, in both tennis and the military,
experience beats everything.

18
00:00:45,170 --> 00:00:46,755
Yes, of course!

19
00:00:47,922 --> 00:00:49,007
-Oh, Clara.
-Yes?

20
00:00:49,090 --> 00:00:50,550
How's the soccer club?

21
00:00:50,633 --> 00:00:53,178
You know us. We're rocking it.

22
00:00:53,261 --> 00:00:56,097
I don't get why
she's coaching the team so hard.

23
00:00:56,181 --> 00:00:58,558
It's just a club, not a pro team.

24
00:00:58,641 --> 00:01:01,478
That way, I can pass out
as soon as I get home.

25
00:01:01,561 --> 00:01:03,146
-And it's fun, right?
-Yeah.

26
00:01:03,229 --> 00:01:06,357
Pass out as soon as you get home?
What about me?

27
00:01:06,441 --> 00:01:09,027
Come on, it's not like we do it every day.

28
00:01:09,861 --> 00:01:12,113
Is this dirty talk I'm hearing?

29
00:01:12,197 --> 00:01:14,032
-I wonder how we got here.
-Do what?

30
00:01:14,115 --> 00:01:15,366
What do they do?

31
00:01:15,450 --> 00:01:16,534
Stop it!

32
00:01:16,618 --> 00:01:17,535
Min-ho's here.

33
00:01:17,619 --> 00:01:18,703
What is it they do?

34
00:01:19,537 --> 00:01:20,371
Do what?

35
00:01:20,455 --> 00:01:23,875
Listen, I'll be officiating
your nuptial Mass, okay?

36
00:01:24,501 --> 00:01:25,460
Thank you in advance.

37
00:01:25,543 --> 00:01:27,128
Hello, Father!

38
00:01:27,212 --> 00:01:29,380
-Hi, kids.
-Thank you!

39
00:01:30,090 --> 00:01:34,094
When the time stands still
You're asleep, I come to you

40
00:01:34,177 --> 00:01:38,056
The world gets in my way
But I end up by your side

41
